er3.cfm%3Fid%3D1561606490503%26author%3D%25E6%25B1%259F%25E8%25BF%2585&d=P86Nric8SGsb572WK9RGd7500bRp0Z5eW4%2BYbKsxGJA%3D&h=d4b8d59a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.yzzk.com/cfm/blogger3.cfm?id=1561606490503&amp;author=%E6%B1%9F%E8%BF%85</a><br />\n<br />\n希望局方以電郵書面回覆本人之投訴。<br />\n<br />\n香港市民<br />\n<br />\n副本送:<br />\n公務員事務局助理秘書長(品行紀律)<br />\n高級首席行政主任(紀律秘書處)<br />\n總行政主任(品行紀律)1<br />\n總行政主任(品行紀律)2<br />\n高級行政主任(品行紀律)1<br />\n高級行政主任(品行紀律)2<br />\n高級行政主任(品行紀律)3<br />\n高級行政主任(品行紀律)4<br />\n高級行政主任(品行紀律)5<br />\n高級行政主任(品行紀律)6"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T04:40:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>任何有關警員既投訴，公務員事務局會發番比警察投訴課/警監會。任何有關公務員對自己部門/局管理層既投訴，會發番比佢個局/部門。擺明<br />\n自己人查自己人， 唔撚做野，唔好比公務員事務局呢個維穩機器繼續， 一定要challenge番佢跟據相關條例佢係要跟進！！！！</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"4d6f7398102698ec25686a20f0936cd646a8ae8a","tid":1370497,"uid":146813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T04:50:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f6fa61837cdcd39106ceade33404ed5225136322","tid":1370497,"uid":59450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T04:52:22.000Z","msg":"做嘢"},{"pid":"29f4f5b2c5b1e1a7394875560655735a8d51c683","tid":1370497,"uid":36089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T04:52:41.000Z","msg":"唔好意思，借一借位～<br />\n<br />\n大家今日出街一定要帶哨子，長遮！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dqQbmS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dqQbmS</a>"},{"pid":"298bee75cf6efda09c800d79ddf10dfcaf22f320","tid":1370497,"uid":18639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T04:53:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2b3c3f485c63703caa145241d6e6433c680a97d","tid":1370497,"uid":47905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T04:53:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"95a1272bc4126c8e4ae8e21b5dc89d3f283111af","tid":1370497,"uid":9315,"like":0,"dislike":